{"tid":646094,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老公家姐（姑奶）不為人知的秘密，好嘔心","createTime":"2018-04-28T17:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T04:51:36.000Z","uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b40dbc8c921382d2f9e0bfd8f0ab46d56661de8","tid":646094,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"老公有3個家姐，昨晚老公無端端爆響口，話佢個大家姐後生時做過 Web J 養條仔，6299唔知情，只有佢地幾姐弟知，跟手我今日上網根據當時資料搵一搵，嘩，原來佢係做色情網站 Web J，直頭係一絲不掛，擘大髀仲要近鏡，好嘔心，現在段片仲可以隨時係網上睇到，真係以後見到佢唔知點算好， 又或者俾朋友知道佢係我大姑奶，我塊面唔知放係邊？仲有，我都有細佬妹，我真係不能想像俾自己細佬妹睇到全相會點，總之好嘔心啦。"},{"pid":"8a069f3f9b612becb0b354dece348b4dce3c879c","tid":646094,"uid":75137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"我都有收埋少少 web j相同片<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾我撞到佢地/fb 唔係一定send哂俾佢d親朋戚友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做雞係到付出代價嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696aa1fb2671b21716b34829579ceb2f62cdb66d","tid":646094,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"咁怕，去其他國家定居吧。"},{"pid":"4c99eac94d2ed4065b78d266831d4c964cf08ab2","tid":646094,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b246b483e4810864827e0edefffcaba38f9a82","tid":646094,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:52:48.000Z","msg":"現在段片仲可以隨時係網上睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bafb6a8c23b2dfd0e0a86a839464d055871baf","tid":646094,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50b246b483e4810864827e0edefffcaba38f9a82","tid":646094,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:52:48.000Z","msg":"現在段片仲可以隨時係網上睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:55:14.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"2fc3515a8b186d70df4e6